                    At Lev Academic, we believe that there is no “one size fits
                    all” approach when choosing the right journals to submit
                    your work to. We believe that traditionally dominating
                    decision drivers such as the impact factor should only be
                    one element of the wider decision-making process. Instead,
                    we take a unique holistic approach, factoring in your niche,
                    needs and preferences to recommend the right journals for
                    you to work with.

